nativeapptext: One or more errors was found at trying to use CSV File:
English: One or more errors was found at trying to use CSV File:\n
Português: Um ou mais erros foram encontrados ao tentar usar o arquivo CSV:

nativeapptext: 01 - All the rows have to have the same number of columns.\nMake sure to select the correct delimiter and quote char. If the set quote char is an empty value, it will not recognize any other quote char inside the CSV file.
English: 01 - All the rows have to have the same number of columns.\nMake sure to select the correct delimiter and quote char. If the set quote char is an empty value, it will not recognize any other quote char inside the CSV file.
Português: 01 – Todas as linhas precisam ter o mesmo número de colunas. Certifique-se de selecionar os delimitadores corretos. Se o delimitador de texto configurado é um valor vazio, ele não irá reconhecer qualquer outro delimitador dentro do arquivo CSV.

nativeapptext: 02 - The selected field can not be used as primary key because there are rows with repeated values. Delete rows with empty value as well.
English: 02 - The selected field can not be used as primary key because there are rows with repeated values. Delete rows with empty value as well.
Português: 02 – O campo selecionado não pode ser usado como chave primária porque há linhas com valores repetidos.  Exclua linhas com valores vazios também.
